Performance Notes:
Recall was strong overall. Main corrections involved remembering the exact phrasing of “¿Hasta qué hora está abierto?” and agreement with feminine nouns such as “La moto no es cómoda.” Past-tense phrases involving “había cambiado de idea” and “ha cambiado de idea” were recalled correctly, showing improved retention compared to previous days.

